content: The **list of [cathedrals](/wiki/Cathedral) in [Singapore](/wiki/Singapore)**, sorted by [denominations](/wiki/Christian_denomination), is as follows: ## Catholicism - [Cathedral of the Good Shepherd](/wiki/Cathedral_of_the_Good_Shepherd), [Civic District](/wiki/Civic_District) ## Anglicanism - [St. Andrew's Cathedral](/wiki/St_Andrew%27s_Cathedral,_Singapore), [Downtown Core](/wiki/Downtown_Core) ## Eastern Orthodoxy - Holy Resurrection Cathedral of Singapore - [List of cathedrals](/wiki/List_of_cathedrals) - [Christianity in Singapore](/wiki/Christianity_in_Singapore)
title: List of cathedrals in Singapore
